title: [Deep Forest, Path]
description: Within the forest's heart, the pungent mustiness of loam rules hand in hand with the relentless green of the woods.  A ragged path winds its way through boles of trees growing so closely together, they look almost like a solid wall.  Chinks of green light filter down from the intertwined branches overhead and sway gently at the prompt of a breeze, dappling the trail where it can be seen through the overhang of fern fronds.

Within the forest's heart, the pungent mustiness of loam rules hand in hand with the relentless green of the woods.  A ragged path winds its way through boles of trees growing so closely together, they look almost like a solid wall.  Soft, green-tinged moonlight filters down from the intertwined branches overhead, dappling the trail where it can be seen through the encroaching shadows of fern fronds.
